wiki.summary: "There's Nothing Holdin' Me Back" is a song recorded by Canadian singer and songwriter Shawn Mendes, written by Mendes, Teddy Geiger, Geoff Warburton and Scott Harris,[1] produced by Geiger, and mixed by Andrew Maury. The song was included in the reissue of his second studio album Illuminate. It was released as a single on April 20, 2017. The song's accompanying music video was released on June 21. Read more on Last.fm.
